  <h2>Introduction</h2>
  <p>
    CivMods ("we", "us", or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy in compliance with the
    General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR). This Privacy Policy explains our practices regarding the
    collection, use, and disclosure of information when you use our desktop application and related services accessible
